cuems-audioplayer (0.0.3-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Updated for Debian Bookworm
  * Integrated cuems-mediadecoder submodule
  * Added video file audio playback support
  * Fixed MTC synchronization race conditions (atomic variables)
  * Improved audio channel downmixing (only when necessary, like mpv)
  * Fixed audio glitches with DTS multi-channel playback
  * Added comprehensive test suite with Google Test
  * Improved device selection and sample rate detection
  * Added pw-jack compatibility for PipeWire users
  * Updated copyright notices and mpv acknowledgment

 -- Ion Reguera <ion@stagelab.coop>  Mon, 24 Nov 2025 20:11:58 +0100

